net.shibboleth.utilities.java.support.collection

Class LockableClassToInstanceMultiMap<B>

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.shibboleth.utilities.java.support.collection.ClassToInstanceMultiMap<B>
      • net.shibboleth.utilities.java.support.collection.LockableClassToInstanceMultiMap<B>
  • Type Parameters:
    B - a bound for the types of values in the map

    public class LockableClassToInstanceMultiMap<B>
extends ClassToInstanceMultiMap<B>
    A specialization of ClassToInstanceMultiMap which exposes a map-specific instance of ReadWriteLock. Callers of the map are responsible for explicitly locking (and unlocking) for reading and/or writing, based on application use cases and concurrency requirements.
